step.context:
\text{If }I=\int \dfrac{\cos x}{\sqrt{1 + \sin x}}\,dx 
= \int \dfrac{1}{\sqrt{t}} \, dt   \\
\text{Does this look correct?}

step.tex:
\begin{align}
  I &= \int \dfrac{1}{\sqrt{t}} \, dt  \\
    &= \dfrac{t^{1/2}}{1/2} + C \\
    &= 2 \sqrt t + C \\
    &= 2\sqrt{1 + \sin x} + C

\end{align}

\begin{align}
  I &= \int \dfrac{1}{\sqrt{t}} \, dt  \\
    &= \dfrac{1}{2} \cdot t^{1/2} + C \\
    &= \dfrac{1}{2} \sqrt t + C \\
    &= \dfrac{1}{2} \sqrt{1 + \sin x} + C

\end{align}
